<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She may be hunkering down in Australia.</p>

<p>But Nicole Kidman made sure to tune in to watch her country star husband Keith Urban live as he hosted the ACM Awards in Nashville this Wednesday.</p>

<p>The 53-year-old platinum blonde actress shared a sweet Instagram clip of herself beaming as she watched the show on a laptop.</p>

<p>Best wishes from Byron Bay: Nicole Kidman made sure to tune in to watch her country star husband Keith Urban live as he hosted the ACM Awards in Nashville this Wednesday</p>

<p>'Wishing I was there, but streaming <?php echo e('@'); ?>KeithUrban on the #ACMAwards here in #ByronBay [heart] #Nashville,' she wrote in her caption. </p>

<p>'I believe it’s about community,' Keith could be seen saying onstage in the segment of the show Nicole was watching. </p>

<p>'The songs, the stories and the artists that tell ‘em – they bring us healing, comfort, and they bring hope and we sure could use some of that right about now, don’t you think?' he asked the audience watching at home.</p>

<p>The awards show extravaganza blends live and pre-taped segments and be held across three Nashville landmarks, facilitating social distancing. </p>

<p>Hot couple: Nicole and Keith, who rang in their 14th wedding anniversary this summer, are pictured attending the CMA Awards in Nashville last November</p>

<p>One was the Grand Ole Opry where Keith performed his hosting duties and the others were the Ryman Auditorium and Bluebird Cafe. </p>

<p>The Grand Ole Opry was celebrating 95 years since its foundation, as marked by Carrie Underwood in a medley of songs by legendary country ladies.</p>

<p>Her barnstorming performance that evening included nods to such icons as Dolly Parton, Patsy Cline, Reba McEntire and Loretta Lynn.</p>

<p>Keith and Nicole were first introduced to one another in January 2005 at G'Day LA, an event for Hollywood Australians, and they married in Sydney on June 25, 2006. </p>

<p>Making it happen: The awards show extravaganza blends live and pre-taped segments and be held across three Nashville landmarks, facilitating social distancing</p>

<p>Place to be: One was the Grand Ole Opry where Keith performed his hosting duties and the others were the Ryman Auditorium and Bluebird Cafe</p>

<p>Both of them are Australians - Keith was born in New Zealand but raised outside Brisbane, while Nicole was born in Honolulu and brought up in Sydney. </p>

<p>Before her romance with Keith she was married to her Eyes Wide Shut co-star Tom Cruise with whom she adopted her children Isabella, 27, and Connor, 25. </p>

<p>She and Keith have gone on to have two more daughters together - a 12-year-old called Sunday and a nine-year-old called Faith. </p>

